Hitachi Plans to Open Czech Auto Parts Plant, Hospodarske Says

-- B y   L a d k a   B a u e r o v a
-- 
2011-06-08T06:07:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/hitachi-plans-to-open-czech-auto-parts-plant-hospodarske-says.html
Hitachi Ltd. (6501)  plans to open an auto
parts production plant near the Czech town of Zatec,  Lidove
Noviny  reported, citing CzechInvest, the government agency for
promoting investment.  The plant is scheduled to open in the spring of 2012 and
will employ 224 people, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladka Bauerova in Prague at 
 lbauerova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Kennedy at   wkennedy3@bloomberg.net  